text=Recycled+Dress\" alt=\"Recycled Dress\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h4>Upcycled Denim Dress</h4>\n                    <p>A unique, one-of-a-kind dress crafted from recycled denim.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$120.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/34495e/ffffff?text=Hemp+Pants\" alt=\"Hemp Pants\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h4>Durable Hemp Trousers</h4>\n                    <p>Comfortable and hard-wearing trousers made from natural hemp fibers.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$95.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container section\" style=\"background-color: #eaf2f5; padding: 50px 20px; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color: #2c3e50;\">Get In Touch</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; color: #34495e;\">Have questions or want to learn more about our practices?</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; color: #34495e;\">Email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\" style=\"color: #2c3e50; text-decoration: underline;\">info@evergreenthreads.com</a></p>\n    </section>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}